      • getIds

        public java.util.List<java.lang.String> getIds(PublicationIDType type)
        Retrieves all external IDs stored in this publication record matching the given type. Querying for PublicationIDType.DBLP will just return a single-item list with the same ID result as Record.getKey().
        Parameters:
        type - The ID type.
        Returns:
        The IDs.
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the specified type is null.

      • idTypes

        public java.util.stream.Stream<PublicationIDType> idTypes()
        Retrieves a sequential stream of all external ID types stored in this publication record. The internal type PublicationIDType.DBLP will be ignored by this method.
        Returns:
        The stream of types.

      • getXml

        public java.lang.String getXml()
        Description copied from class: Record
        Return the dblp XML element of this record as a String.

        Non-ASCII characters in the text content of the returned XML are not escaped (i.e., it's encoded as Java UTF-16).

        Specified by:
        getXml in class Record
        Returns:
        The dblp record as a String.
